snippet.title: City of Tomorrow: Brawl Pass! Knockout City Season 6
snippet.description: Let's hear it for the return of the Brawl Pass, an exciting way to earn up to 100 additional rewards in a Season by earning XP and completing Brawl Pass Contracts! And you’re going to want to put in the work to earn XP and complete those Brawl Pass Contracts because it’s the only way you’ll hear the story that unfolds in the Deep Space Dispatches. The DSD is the only way you can hear the lore behind Knockout City, so get ready to work your way to level 100, and get the scoop on what's going down in the City of Tomorrow!
